# PipingBox — Environment variables example
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the real values.
# NEVER commit `.env.local` (it is gitignored).
#
# Vite exposes only variables prefixed with VITE_ to the client.
# The Supabase anon key is PUBLIC by design — it is safe in client code
# as long as Row-Level Security (RLS) is enforced (DEC-07).
# See: brain/03-ENGINEERING/DEPLOYMENT.md and brain/00-FOUNDATION/CTO_MEMORY.md (DEC-36, TD-01).

# Supabase project URL (without trailing slash)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-ref.supabase.co

# Supabase anon public key (safe to expose client-side; protected by RLS)
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here
